Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:44.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ありがてぇ　スモモか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:52.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おう　ふたば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:01.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大きくなったな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:03.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お帰り　幹太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:11.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今度はどんな所行ってたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,東のでっかい町でな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:17.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ズラリと立派な屋敷の並ぶところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そこで一番の屋敷を建ててきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まるで竜宮城みたいでな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:29.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子　寂しがってたわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:34.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう少し　近くで仕事したら？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたの腕なら　どこでだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:43.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺は知らない土地を　腕一本で渡ってくのが面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:47.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,世の中にゃ　本当にいろんなところがあるもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:54.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう少し　年を喰ったら落ち着くからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夢か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,偉くはっきりとした夢だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まただ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また　あの木の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:01.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体　何なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:14.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でもあの木　なんだか見覚えがあるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,杉の巨木？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:23.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　幹周りが大人の男で五六人分ありそうな…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　そんなのここらじゃ聞かねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:37.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,邪魔するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:43.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた　どっかで会ったことがあるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうかい　こっちには覚えはねぇが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　間違いねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたは山の中を五六人と連れ立って歩いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それからまた山ん中を歩いてった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたは十ほどの子供だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一行にゃもう一人子供がいたな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それから長老の爺さん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの爺さんは子供のころからよく見た顔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:14.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい待て　何で爺さんの子供のころなんて知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:16.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前　年いくつだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そういやそうだな　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何で俺こんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰かに聞いたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　出鱈目言ってんじゃねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何か急に思い出したというか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,新手のペテンなら　もう少しうまくやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　違うんだよ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,里ができてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:15.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この里　どこかで見た
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見覚えがあるわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:32.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは　この山から見た俺の里だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,木は　この辺りのはず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これでようやく謎が解ける
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これ…か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さて　帰るか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,抜けねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　誰かいないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,た　助けてくれ　足が…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,遅かったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さんに会った後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ふと思い当たることがあってな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一人の人が知りえるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ある一定の場所の　遥か昔の出来事を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まるで　その目で見てきたかのように
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,つぶさに語る者がいる…と
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:23.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,な　何でこんなことになった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まるで足が木になっちまったみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ぴくりともしねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:33.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,スモモに似た赤い実を先頃食ったはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつは　「覚木」という蟲でした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:43.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,木の内部に宿り　養分を得るものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:48.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,木の本体が危機に陥ると　赤い花のようなものをつけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やがてひとつの実に姿を変えて　木から離れる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:57.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その実には　木の記憶が封じ込められている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして　獣や鳥に食われると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:06.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その体内に巣食い　宿主が木に近づくのを待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,宿主が木に長い間触れていると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,木と融合し動けなくさせ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やがて完全に木と同化させてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それで　どうすればこの足は治るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:25.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,治す術は見つかっていない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,宿主が危険に曝されれば出ていくんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:32.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら　死ぬふりをしたらどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:38.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,花をつけることはあっても　実をつけて抜けることはないという
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:45.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,覚木には　本当の危機とそれ以外とを見極める能力があるらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,恐らく　それを見極めるために
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,木の膨大な記憶を利用するのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:58.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　何か手はないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こんな　こんな足じゃ俺はどうやって…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,幹太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:08.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私はあんたの命が奪われずに済んで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それだけでありがたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家族みんなで助けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,冗談じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,みんなの世話になって生きてくなんでまっぴらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ　頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,治してくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,僅かな手がかりでもあればいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの時のあの木　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,切られちまったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:11.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この木は千年もここに立ち続けているという
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イサザ　ちゃんと聞かんか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:19.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だって俺　この話何度も聞いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何度でも聞け　忘れんように
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:29.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前もいずれ　若い渡りに言い伝えられるようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:36.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この木にはもう長いこと　覚木が住んどる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:42.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつは今までに　二度ほど　赤い花をつけたことがあるという
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これがその花だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:52.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一度目に咲いたのは　五百五十年ほど昔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この地に大地震のあったとき
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:01.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,地が割れ　根から倒れそうになったが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:03.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何とか生き延びたという
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,二度目は　百七十年ほど前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この木に雷が落ちり　傷を負った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:20.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　近くの里の者たちが懸命にその傷を治し
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:23.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,再びこの木は生き長らえた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:28.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　あそこに見える里だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:34.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの里の者らがここへ来たのは三百年ほど前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:40.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山を開くのにこの木を切ろうとしたが　どうやっても切れなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:44.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それで人々はこの木を恐れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:49.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やがて神木と祭り　大事にしたのだという
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:53.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここは光脈筋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:58.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,長くそこに生きた木は時に特殊な力を持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人の力が及ばんこともある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:08.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,わしも子供の頃からいろんな巨木を見てきたが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これほど大きく見える木はそうはない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:19.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　この頃はこの木を訪れる里の者の姿は減った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:24.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつが少々気にかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,かつてはご神木だったそうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:45.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ　それは立派な木でしたから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それがなぜこんなことに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:54.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,皆　怯えていたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:13:00.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このままではきっと里は終わりだと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:05.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは今から15年ほど前　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:11.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,当時　里の大半の者が杣人として木を育て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,売ることを生業としていました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,皆起きろ　大変じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山が…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体　どうすりゃいい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう頼る当てもねぇ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,里を下りて物乞いをやるしか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:46.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,な　あの大杉　町の材木商が大金で買いたいと言ってたろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか　あの木は無事だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　あの木は…なぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それに絶対切れないって話だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなもの　やってみなけりゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おう　やろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:02.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　待たんか　お前たち
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:06.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これ以上待てねぇ　うちの子はこのままじゃ死んじまう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うちもだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:12.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの木は先祖は代々大事にしてきたご神木だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当に切れなきゃ諦めるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:17.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　あの花は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだか恐ろしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:30.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,木が怒っているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何を言っている　どこに花なんか　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いい加減なことを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　止せ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,切れるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　切れないなんて迷信だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:21.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ　この水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どんどん広がっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:36.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その木は里全体がしばし暮らせる程の額で売れました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:42.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして　焼けた山も不思議な速さで蘇っていきました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:49.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,当時　幼かった幹太が無事に育ったのも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この木のおかげなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:56.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああしなければ　今の里はなかったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:03.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　あの時やはりこの木は怒っていたのでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:08.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これは報いなんでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,草木は怒ったりしませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:17.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　何も感じないわけでも　何もしないわけでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:22.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ある種の木は害虫が大量に湧くと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その葉から毒を出して自分の身を守る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:28.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,草木は自ら動けない　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だがその分　周囲の変化を敏感に感じ取り
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,時にそれに応じて自らを変える術を持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:41.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この木には人の斧を寄せ付けないほどの力があった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それがなぜその時は切れたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それはこの木が自ら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その身を切られるよう変化させたせいなのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,傷ついた山全体のために
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,木がそんなことを…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さてね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もしそうだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:16.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私達は本当に大事なものを失くしてしまったんだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これを飲んでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それで足が治るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　蟲の成長を抑えるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:32.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,足の治療法は知人にいろいろ文を出してみたが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,良い返事のものはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これからも調査を続けてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,別の蟲師に当ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何かあったら　ここに文をくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:08.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ　お外行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまんな　父ちゃんはもう前のようには…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ　お話して
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:19.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう　してやれる話もないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの木のせいでなぜ俺がこんな目に…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,とうに切られた木のくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なぜいつまでも俺の中に居座り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,赤い…花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さん　体の具合はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　別に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら　何か起こる前兆だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:13.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたの身に危険の及ぶ何か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:30.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だろう　この気配
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:35.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,草木が騒いでいる　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この気配は知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:45.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,遥か　遥か昔に一度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,思い出せ　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,思い出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの時　何が起こったか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,え　何だって？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今すぐ全員集まれとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何なんだ　一体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,とにかく急げって　幹太が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここらでいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　ここらは危ない　まだ先だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:22.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,急がねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もうじきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よう　調子はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見ての通りだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　この中にいたらと思うとな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,幹太の奴　何で分かったんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それがよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:18.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この間15年前に切ったあの大杉に取り憑かれただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:22.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それ以来偉い昔のことまで知ってるんだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:27.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それがわしのひい爺さんの話と同じでな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:33.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,わしらはまたあの大杉に助けられたのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:39.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,すまないな　自分の家も大変だろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:43.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,気にするな　命の恩人なんだからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:44.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうそう　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:48.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの大杉を切ってしまったことは今でも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:51.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,皆古傷のように残ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:54.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,受けた恩も　もう返せない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だから　お前に返させてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:02.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,困ったことがあったら　里の皆で助ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:06.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,またあの木が教えてくれることがあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:08.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,わしらにも教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:20.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,気の遠くなるような長い長い時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:29.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この地には一本の木が立っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:37.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,深く深く根を下ろし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:47.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,高く広く枝を張り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:55.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この地に生まれては消える者達の移ろいを　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:06.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,変わらず　静かに　見下ろしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:16.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　ふたば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:18.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なーに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:20.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こっちにおいで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:24.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一本の木の話をしようか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:32.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとずっとこの山に立っていた大きな木の
